ope></bibl>, etc.; sts. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴτε . . ἤ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg012.perseus-grc1:897\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">897</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἢ . . εἴτε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:177\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">177</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n46568.10\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> without introductory Particle, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐδέ τι οἶδα ζώει ὅ γ᾽ ἦ τέθνηκε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:464\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.464</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:546\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.546</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:238\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.238</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"B\" id=\"n46568.11\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> COMPARATIVE, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">than, as</tr_>, after a <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href